 If Asc(Mid(inString, x, 1)) > 32 Then inString = Mid(inString, 1, x): Exit For
Next

For x = 1 To Len(inString) Step 1
 If Asc(Mid(inString, x, 1)) < 32 Then Trim32 = Mid(inString, 1, x - 1): Exit Function
Next

Trim32 = inString

End Function

